      "text": "JAMES, J. and BRICKEN, W., 1992. A boundary notation for visual mathematics. In: Proceedings IEEE Workshop on Visual Languages. Online. Seattle, WA, USA: IEEE Comput. Soc. Press. 1992. p. 267–269. [Accessed 31 July 2022]. ISBN 978-0-8186-3090-3. DOI 10.1109/WVL.1992.275745. [https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/stamp/stamp.jsp?arnumber=275745&casa_token=yUVRhqTCvhQAAAAA:Tp8dy5duTNxjL6jSJnMX5fSpk5WFmb_QrR-hdfCntp6NRkwtIx9xRXlrkS5ANtS44OUBTgVK9L0&tag=1 pdf]\n"
